{"tid":1997203,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"幫手睇下係咪隻SSD 壞咗","createTime":"2020-05-01T13:21:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-01T15:02:07.000Z","uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"52d274a964b7b316083207a300a3f1a32e4b7dff","tid":1997203,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:21:43.000Z","msg":"某日開機突然開唔到，卡死咗在 bios(uefi) 畫面，無出任何錯誤聲音。<br />\n<br />\n以下係自己測試過程，部機spec 在最底:<br />\n<br />\n一開始快速設定嘅boot list 唔見咗隻碟，在 advance 入面揾得返出嚟，不過之後都係 load 空氣。<br />\n<br />\n以為係 bcd 同 mbr 壞咗，插開機 usb 入 cmd按網上啲教學行一次 發現一直話揾唔到有 windows ......<br />\n<br />\n諗住打定輸數重裝算，點知一入到揀裝喺邊隻碟時見到原本隻ssd系統碟寫住大約240G 嘅容量<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">，顯示可用空間 同容量一致</span></span>。  <br />\n心諗，咁咪啫係咩都無嘅吉碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n另一隻1TB 嘅HDD data 碟變咗寫住 本機。<br />\n<br />\n重裝返入SSD / 新增磁區在原來 SSD 都不成功。<br />\n出錯誤碼 0x80300002 ，上網爬文見到話可能係太多碟有讀取錯誤。<br />\n<br />\n雖然得2隻碟，都關機斷電後拆咗隻1TB嘅HDD sata 同電線再試過。<br />\n<br />\n都係裝唔到入隻ssd / 分磁區。<br />\n錯誤碼: 0x843ba080<br />\n查唔到係咩<br />\n<br />\n咁嘅話係唔係隻 SSD 收咗皮??<br />\n救教<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n啱啱睇返隻SSD 係kingston ，但<span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">被bios 識別為 satafirm s11</span></span><br />\n覺得怪怪哋，上網查下覺得好似中咗伏?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPS:<br />\n家中長輩機，佢自己出面揾電腦鋪砌嘅。一年左右，呢排發現用壞咗掟過嚟話佢無咩點用過唔知點解壞。<br />\n<br />\n老屈話明明佢上次用都無事，一定係我整壞佢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />..... (明明我都無掂過佢部機)<br />\n<br />\n不過一家人，要頂硬上。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nSpec:<br />\n<br />\n媽媽版: asus prime H110M2<br />\ncpu : i3 - 7100<br />\nram :  OCPC XTREME DDR4 2400 8G x1<br />\n火牛: AcBel CE2 <br />\nSSD: kingston 230G (被bios識別為 satafirm s11)<br />\nHDD: Seagate 1TB ST1000DM003"},{"pid":"fca13faf16eca20f31d20084e0960cf654ece26a","tid":1997203,"uid":204702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:23:43.000Z","msg":"satafirm s11 = YOU FUCKED UP"},{"pid":"9fee9ed8ebc5dc8a43acf916f3a5d7194878b5f4","tid":1997203,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fca13faf16eca20f31d20084e0960cf654ece26a","tid":1997203,"uid":204702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:23:43.000Z","msg":"satafirm s11 = YOU FUCKED UP"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:30:10.000Z","msg":"啫係未過保養可以拆定去等換碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},{"pid":"862345758499f0c7cfce75e46c17fb71cca6c8b2","tid":1997203,"uid":204702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9fee9ed8ebc5dc8a43acf916f3a5d7194878b5f4","tid":1997203,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fca13faf16eca20f31d20084e0960cf654ece26a","tid":1997203,"uid":204702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:23:43.000Z","msg":"satafirm s11 = YOU FUCKED UP"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:30:10.000Z","msg":"啫係未過保養可以拆定去等換碟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:36:15.000Z","msg":"未過保養就快手攞過去做RMA啦"},{"pid":"6d692c25081b3b2285c7b756ab22e38067fdb505","tid":1997203,"uid":73991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"老屈話明明佢上次用都無事，一定係我整壞佢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />..... (明明我都無掂過佢部機)<br />\n<br />\n咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eabfbc42770e427657272428464c20162173c184","tid":1997203,"uid":33874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:55:17.000Z","msg":"壞咗"},{"pid":"9d6b291327d16d73883321fa6e01cdc94868c249","tid":1997203,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T15:00:21.000Z","msg":"thx 大家<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c7bbb40946924ad6fecca390dec0f3f55e9432e","tid":1997203,"uid":335003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6d692c25081b3b2285c7b756ab22e38067fdb505","tid":1997203,"uid":73991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:53:21.000Z","msg":"老屈話明明佢上次用都無事，一定係我整壞佢嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />..... (明明我都無掂過佢部機)<br />\n<br />\n咁仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T15:02:07.000Z","msg":"係咁，老人家興一出事就話一定唔關自己事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n自己部電話唔見咗嘢都覺得一定係有其他人搞佢，一定唔係佢自己㩒錯 (但佢又唔多識用...)"}]}